'''Chinna Karaiyamputhur ({{Lang-ta|<U+0B9A><U+0BBF><U+0BA9><U+0BCD><U+0BA9> <U+0B95><U+0BB0><U+0BC8><U+0BAF><U+0BBE><U+0BAE><U+0BCD><U+0BAA><U+0BC1><U+0BA4><U+0BC2><U+0BB0><U+0BCD>}})''' is a village<ref>http://drda.puducherry.gov.in/images/gplist.pdf</ref> in [[Bahour Commune]] of [[Bahour taluk]]  in the Union Territory of [[Puducherry]], [[India]]. It lies on the eastern part of [[Karaiyamputhur]] Enclave of [[Puducherry]]. Chinna Karaiyamputhur serves as a link between [[Karaiyamputhur]] and [[Manamedu]] Enclave. Chinna Karaiyamputhur is a part of [[Karaiyamputhur]] Village Panchayat.

